metadata.name: Elchai Card NFT #1
metadata.description: Elchai Car Club is bringing the future of cars and luxury to the world's most innovative city, Dubai. Car NFTs is a collection of 3600 NFT that will be available as FREE MINT for the early adopters. These one-of-a-kind digital assets represent access to all the Cars in the collection. NFT Holders will be able to rent 50+ exclusive Hyper Cars.
